snippet.title: Glum: A Wicked Misadventure - Official Announcement Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Glum: A Wicked Misadventure is a first-person boot combat game developed by CinderCat Games. Players are armed with a magical boot to become a true ass-kicking pro as players press on their journey to save the captured overlord. Glum: A Wicked Misadventure is coming soon to PC.

#GLUMAWickedMisadventure #RealmsDeep2023
